OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine end
OL,6,Fto the day with plenty of evening
OL,7,Fsunshine and staying mainly dry
OL,8,Fovernight. Thickening cloud could
OL,9,Fbring patchy rain to Argyll. Winds
OL,10,Fmostly light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FMainly dry and bright with
OL,13,Fhazy sunshine and very warm or hot.
OL,14,FOccasional thicker cloud over Argyll
OL,15,Fcould give the odd burst of rain.
OL,16,FLight winds with sea breezes possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
